  "original_title": "\u0b8a\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b89\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb0\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0ba4 \u0b89\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b86\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sri Lanka Human Rights Commission condemns curfew",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sri Lanka's Human Rights Commission has said that the arbitrary imposition of curfew by the Inspector General of Police is illegal.",
        "The Human Rights Commission has stated that the order to illegally restrict the right to movement has violated the basic rights of the people and has also mentioned that the police officer in charge of that area can restrict the movement if there is a role for peace in a particular area.",
        "The Inspector General of Police issued an illegal order when there was no complaint about the violations, the Inspector General of Police should inform the public about the reason for this order, the Human Rights Commission said that the government is trying to control the demonstrations illegally after failing to get an order to control the demonstration."
      ],
